DOC.brief_summary: The aim of this study is to confirm the difference in ovarian reserve markers and serum vitamine D levels between infertile indian, arabian and caucasian population.
DOC.brief_title: Differences in Ovarian Reserve Markers and Vitamin D Between Infertile Indian, Arabian and Caucasian Population
DOC.criteria: WOMEN BETWEEN 2143 YEARS FIRST OR SECOND IN VITRO FERILIZATION TREATMENT DUE TO TUBAL, MASCULINE OR PREVIOUS INTRAUTERINE INSEMINATION FAIL TREATMENT POLYCYSTIC PATIENTS ENDOMETRIOSIS GRADE III OR IV INFLAMMATORY PELVIC DISEASE
